  <title>What is New and Noteworthy in Drools 5.2.0.M2</title>

  <section>
    <title>Maven artifactId changes</title>

    <para>A couple of maven artifacts (jars, wars, ...) have been renamed so it is more clear what they do. Below is the
    list of the GAV changes, adjust your <literal>pom.xml</literal> files accordingly when upgrading to the new
    version.</para>

